 startup session service, router, and shell behavior for phase 02 batch","status":"pending","priority":"high"},{"content":"Add focused target tests or record concrete harness blocker evidence for phase 02 behavior","status":"pending","priority":"high"},{"content":"Run bounded verification commands for phase 02 and capture outcomes","status":"pending","priority":"high"},{"content":"Update source coverage matrix and platform capability records for completed batch groups","status":"pending","priority":"high"}],"truncated":false},"title":"5 todos","time":{"start":1782363821786,"end":1782363821789}},"id":"prt_efd29959f001ou3F3Fe24T22Gu","sessionID":"ses_102d761b3ffemoAhTGa77K1yUE","messageID":"msg_efd29292f001fBxcpnayrEtroY"}}
{"type":"text","timestamp":1782363821931,"sessionID":"ses_102d761b3ffemoAhTGa77K1yUE","part":{"id":"prt_efd298ca2001494g4JG9BhRT34","messageID":"msg_efd29292f001fBxcpnayrEtroY","sessionID":"ses_102d761b3ffemoAhTGa77K1yUE","type":"text","text":"The phase checklist is consistent and the capability checklist is empty, so I’m moving into source-to-target inspection. One prompt path was stale; I’ll read the protocol from the Kotlin2Cangjie docs path that the workspace planning file points to.","time":{"start":1782363819170,"end":1782363821929}}}
