{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1782364157438,"sessionID":"ses_102d761b3ffemoAhTGa77K1yUE","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_tkOt3XhAEaXACOOAE252zwRl","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\.agents\\skills\\cangjie-harmonyos-doc-search\\tools\\cmd-tools\\cjpm_manual\\项目管理工具\\使用示例.md","offset":1,"limit":220},"output":"<path>D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\.agents\\skills\\cangjie-harmonyos-doc-search\\tools\\cmd-tools\\cjpm_manual\\项目管理工具\\使用示例.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: ## 使用示例\n2: \n3: 以下面仓颉项目的目录结构为例，介绍 `cjpm` 的使用方法，该目录下对应的源码文件示例可见[源代码](#示例的源代码)。该仓颉项目的模块名为 `test`。\n4: \n5: ```text\n6: cj_project\n7: ├── pro0\n8: │    ├── cjpm.toml\n9: │    └── src\n10: │         ├── zoo\n11: │         │    ├── zoo.cj\n12: │         │    └── zoo_test.cj\n13: │         └── pro0.cj\n14: ├── src\n15: │    ├── koo\n16: │    │    ├── koo.cj\n17: │    │    └── koo_test.cj\n18: │    ├── main.cj\n19: │    └── main_test.cj\n20: └── cjpm.toml\n21: ```\n22: \n23: ### init、build 的使用\n24: \n25: - 新建仓颉项目并编写源码 `xxx.cj` 文件，如示例结构所示的 `koo` 包和 `main.cj` 文件。\n26: \n27:     ```shell\n28:     cjpm init --name test --path ./cj_project\n29:     cd cj_project\n30:     mkdir src/koo\n31:     ```\n32: \n33:     此时，会在当前执行命令的目录下创建 `cj_project` 目录，并在该目录中自动生成 `src` 文件夹和默认的 `cjpm.toml` 配置文件。开发者可以自行在源码目录 `src` 中新建子包（如 `src/koo`），或是自行在各包中新增源码文件和测试文件。\n34: \n35: - 当前模块需要依赖外部的 `pro0` 模块时，可以新建 `pro0` 模块及该模块的配置文件，接下来编写该模块的源码文件，需要自行在 `pro0` 下新建 `src` 文件夹，在 `src` 下新建 `pro0` 的 root 包 `pro0.cj`，并将编写的仓颉包放置在 `src` 下，如示例结构所示的 `zoo` 包。\n36: \n37:     ```shell\n38:     mkdir pro0 && cd pro0\n39:     cjpm init --name pro0 --type=static\n40:     mkdir src/zoo\n41:     ```\n42: \n43: - 主模块依赖 `pro0` 时，需要按照手册说明去配置主模块配置文件的 `dependencies` 字段。配置无误后，执行 `cjpm build` 即可，生成的可执行文件在 `target/release/bin/` 目录下。\n44: \n45:     ```shell\n46:     cd cj_project\n47:     vim cjpm.toml\n48:     cjpm build\n49:     cjpm run\n50:     ```\n51: \n52: ### test、clean 的使用\n53: \n54: - 按示例结构，编写完每个文件对应的 `xxx_test.cj` 单元测试文件后，可以执行下述代码进行单元测试，生成的文件在 `target/release/unittest_bin` 目录下。\n55: \n56:     ```shell\n57:     cjpm test\n58:     ```\n59: \n60:     或者\n61: \n62:     ```shell\n63:     cjpm test src src/koo pro0/src/zoo\n64:     ```\n65: \n66: - 想要手动删除 `target` 、`cov_output` 文件夹、`*.gcno` 、`*.gcda` 等中间件时，执行如下命令：\n67: \n68:     ```shell\n69:     cjpm clean\n70:     ```\n71: \n72: ### 示例的源代码\n73: \n74: ```cangjie\n75: // cj_project/src/main.cj\n76: package test\n77: \n78: import pro0.zoo.*\n79: import test.koo.*\n80: \n81: main(): Int64 {\n82:     let res = z + k\n83:     println(res)\n84:     let res2 = concatM(\"a\", \"b\")\n85:     println(res2)\n86:     return 0\n87: }\n88: \n89: func concatM(s1: String, s2: String): String {\n90:     return s1 + s2\n91: }\n92: ```\n93: \n94: ```cangjie\n95: // cj_project/src/main_test.cj\n96: package test\n97: \n98: import std.unittest.* // testfame\n99: import std.unittest.testmacro.* // macro_Defintion\n100: \n101: @Test\n102: public class TestM{\n103:     @TestCase\n104:     func sayhi(): Unit {\n105:         @Assert(concatM(\"1\", \"2\"), \"12\")\n106:         @Assert(concatM(\"1\", \"3\"), \"13\")\n107:     }\n108: }\n109: ```\n110: \n111: ```cangjie\n112: // cj_project/src/koo/koo.cj\n113: package test.koo\n114: \n115: public let k: Int32 = 12\n116: \n117: func concatk(s1: String, s2: String): String {\n118:     return s1 + s2\n119: }\n120: ```\n121: \n122: ```cangjie\n123: // cj_project/src/koo/koo_test.cj\n124: package test.koo\n125: \n126: import std.unittest.* // testfame\n127: import std.unittest.testmacro.* // macro_Defintion\n128: \n129: @Test\n130: public class TestK{\n131:     @TestCase\n132:     func sayhi(): Unit {\n133:         @Assert(concatk(\"1\", \"2\"), \"12\")\n134:         @Assert(concatk(\"1\", \"3\"), \"13\")\n135:     }\n136: }\n137: ```\n138: \n139: ```cangjie\n140: // cj_project/pro0/src/pro0.cj\n141: package pro0\n142: ```\n143: \n144: ```cangjie\n145: // cj_project/pro0/src/zoo/zoo.cj\n146: package pro0.zoo\n147: \n148: public let z: Int32 = 26\n149: \n150: func concatZ(s1: String, s2: String): String {\n151:     return s1 + s2\n152: }\n153: ```\n154: \n155: ```cangjie\n156: // cj_project/pro0/src/zoo/zoo_test.cj\n157: package pro0.zoo\n158: \n159: import std.unittest.* // testfame\n160: import std.unittest.testmacro.* // macro_Defintion\n161: \n162: @Test\n163: public class TestZ{\n164:     @TestCase\n165:     func sayhi(): Unit {\n166:         @Assert(concatZ(\"1\", \"2\"), \"12\")\n167:         @Assert(concatZ(\"1\", \"3\"), \"13\")\n168:     }\n169: }\n170: ```\n171: \n172: ```toml\n173: # cj_project/cjpm.toml\n174: [package]\n175: cjc-version = \"1.0.0\"\n176: description = \"nothing here\"\n177: version = \"1.0.0\"\n178: name = \"test\"\n179: output-type = \"executable\"\n180: \n181: [dependencies]\n182: pro0 = { path = \"pro0\" }\n183: ```\n184: \n185: ```toml\n186: # cj_project/pro0/cjpm.toml\n187: [package]\n188: cjc-version = \"1.0.0\"\n189: description = \"nothing here\"\n190: version = \"1.0.0\"\n191: name = \"pro0\"\n192: output-type = \"static\"\n193: ```\n\n(End of file - total 193 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"## 使用示例\n\n以下面仓颉项目的目录结构为例，介绍 `cjpm` 的使用方法，该目录下对应的源码文件示例可见[源代码](#示例的源代码)。该仓颉项目的模块名为 `test`。\n\n```text\ncj_project\n├── pro0\n│    ├── cjpm.toml\n│    └── src\n│         ├── zoo\n│         │    ├── zoo.cj\n│         │    └── zoo_test.cj\n│         └── pro0.cj\n├── src\n│    ├── koo\n│    │    ├── koo.cj\n│    │    └── koo_test.cj\n│    ├── main.cj\n│    └── main_test.cj\n└── cjpm.toml","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":".agents\\skills\\cangjie-harmonyos-doc-search\\tools\\cmd-tools\\cjpm_manual\\项目管理工具\\使用示例.md","time":{"start":1782364157424,"end":1782364157436}},"id":"prt_efd2eb5c5001jKyLxE7L3gaICs","sessionID":"ses_102d761b3ffemoAhTGa77K1yUE","messageID":"msg_efd2a81d2001ePRwsA8325KXr6"}}
